# Supabase — MusicPro shared project

Copy to `.env.local`:

```env
# MusicPro Eventi Pro (shared with APP GAS)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://fvxdghqpavdcohczrvsc.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key

# App
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Optional — venue for auto-created DEMO01 (else first row in public.venues)
# LOVE_ROULETTE_DEMO_VENUE_ID=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
```

Migrations live in `musicpro-eventi-app/supabase/migrations/` — not in this folder.

Love Roulette resolves events via:

- `events.game_format = 'love_roulette'`
- `events.metadata->>'love_roulette_code'` (6-char URL slug)
- or event UUID in the path

Runtime state: `love_roulette_sessions.runtime_state`
